Quick exponentiation *
Time limit	1 second
Memory limit	64Mb
Input	standard input or input.txt
Output	standard output or output.txt
You can raise the power much faster than in n multiplications! Use the following recurrence relations: a n = (a 2) n / 2 with even n, a n = a cdot a n-1 for odd n. Implement a quick exponentiation algorithm. If you do everything right, then the complexity of your algorithm will be O ( log n).

Input format
Input a real number a and an integer n

Output format
Output answer for the task

Sample 1
Input	Output
2
1
2
Sample 2
Input	Output
2
2
4
Sample 3
Input	Output
2
3
8
